an consciousness itself.", "tokens": [50365, 2053, 412, 577, 428, 1065, 1952, 4675, 1985, 13, 2053, 412, 1952, 10081, 2564, 13, 50601], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1376341651467716, "compression_ratio": 1.734006734006734, "no_speech_prob": 2.0364755888568897e-12}, {"id": 882, "seek": 304678, "start": 3051.5, "end": 3055.5800000000004, "text": " When you sit down and try to remember your past, or when you close your eyes and try to predict your", "tokens": [50601, 1133, 291, 1394, 760, 293, 853, 281, 1604, 428, 1791, 11, 420, 562, 291, 1998, 428, 2575, 293, 853, 281, 6069, 428, 50805], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1376341651467716, "compression_ratio": 1.734006734006734, "no_speech_prob": 2.0364755888568897e-12}, {"id": 883, "seek": 304678, "start": 3055.5800000000004, "end": 3059.5, "text": " tomorrow, are you accessing a perfect, complete state of your brain?", "tokens": [50805, 4153, 11, 366, 291, 26440, 257, 2176, 11, 3566, 1785, 295, 428, 3567, 30, 51001], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1376341651467716, "compression_ratio": 1.734006734006734, "no_speech_prob": 2.0364755888568897e-12}, {"id": 884, "seek": 304678, "start": 3059.5, "end": 3060.86, "text": " You definitely aren't.", "tokens": [51001, 509, 2138, 3212, 380, 13, 51069], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1376341651467716, "compression_ratio": 1.734006734006734, "no_speech_prob": 2.0364755888568897e-12}, {"id": 885, "seek": 304678, "start": 3060.86, "end": 3067.5800000000004, "text": " Do you have perfect, frictionless information about your own life? Of course not. Your memories are fragmented.", "tokens": [51069, 1144, 291, 362, 2176, 11, 17710, 1832, 1589, 466, 428, 1065, 993, 30, 2720, 1164, 406, 13, 2260, 8495, 366, 9241, 14684, 13, 51405], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1376341651467716, "compression_ratio": 1.734006734006734, "no_speech_prob": 2.0364755888568897e-12}, {"id": 886, "seek": 304678, "start": 3067.5800000000004, "end": 3073.1000000000004, "text": "